Revision history for Dancer-Logger-ColorConsole

0.0005  Tue Sep  9 11:02:18 WEST 2014
        - Added color to info log level [Pierre Vigier].
        - Added metadata for metacpan et al.

0.0004  Sun Apr  7 16:57:13 WEST 2013
        - require a specific Term::ANSIColor version

0.0003  Fri Jun  8 22:04:09 WEST 2012
        - fix POD encoding.

0.0002  Mon Jul  4 18:04:14 WEST 2011
        - add a proper Changes file
        - color HTTP requests

0.0001  Sun Jul  3 19:54:19 WEST 2011
        First version, released on an unsuspecting world of Dancers.
        - include defaults for the four default levels of logging
          (code/debug/warn/error)
        - support coloring using regular expressions
        - add basic default coloring for response codes (2XX, 4XX and 5XX)
        - support disabling the default coloring schema


